<div type="description" n="monument">
<head>Description of Monument</head>
<p>
Three adjoining fragments of a <rs type="material" key="marmor">white marble</rs> <rs type="objectType"><rs type="objectType">statue base</rs> shaft</rs> with a moulded panel on one face. a, an upper right corner fragment, has lines 1-6 (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.23</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.33</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.30</measure>);
b, a fragment with the left side moulding surviving has lines 6-20 (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.38</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.53</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.34</measure>);
c, the lower part of the block, with moulding surviving on both sides and below, has lines 16-20 (<measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.46</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="width">0.46</measure> × <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="depth">0.54</measure>).</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="text">
<head>Description of Text</head>
<p>
<rs type="execution" key="scalpro">Inscribed</rs> within the panel; the last letter is cut on the moulding in lines 5, 6, 17, 18 and (presumably) 10.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="letters">
<head>Description of Letters</head>
<p>
ll. 1-15. <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.025</measure>; ll 16-20, <measure type="length" unit="metre" dim="height">0.022-0.023</measure>.
</p>
<p>
Ligatures: <foreign lang="grc">ΗΝ</foreign>, l.8; <foreign lang="grc">ΤΗ</foreign>, l.9; <foreign lang="grc">ΝΕ</foreign>, l. 19.</p>
</div>

<div type="description" n="date">
<head>Date</head>
<p>
<date notAfter="0260" exact="both" precision="circa" notBefore="0253">A.D. 253-260</date>
(<rs type="criteria">content</rs>).</p>
</div>

